title: The Cypher
description:
The Cypher is a drop-through board designed to get sideways with lots of features to help you stay that way.
This board includes 1/2" of rocker through the length of the deck, getting you lower to the ground for easier, bigger, and longer power slides. Mellow tub concave and an ample width keep you glued to the deck without cramping your feet or your style, meaning you can keep the style session rolling all day.
L: 38.00"
W: 10.25"
WB: 30.50"
The 2013 Cypher features a Hawaiian Koa bottom sheet with art by Eric Waetzig.
Designed by team rider Duke Degen
Rider: Duke Degen
